title: Tim Corley's Web Portfolio & Blog
author: Tim Corley
description: I am a Software Engineer focused on Quality Assurance & Web Development. I have over 4 years of professional experience as a Test Automation Engineer using Python, Selenium, and Appium. I enjoy building, breaking, and testing things. Other than Python & Selenium, I've got React, TypeScript, GraphQL, NodeJS, and AWS in my development toolkit. Please take a look around - check out some of my projects, browse my blog posts, and always feel free to get in touch.
